=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Key => Str

The name of the attribute.

The following attribute is supported by Network Load Balancers, and
Gateway Load Balancers.

=over

=item *

C<tcp.idle_timeout.seconds> - The tcp idle timeout value, in seconds.
The valid range is 60-6000 seconds. The default is 350 seconds.

=back

The following attributes are only supported by Application Load
Balancers.

